# Pamela single and multi-line elements hint information
<document

  <single:This is a single line element, text only

  <single:This is a single line element, <span:with additional element>
  <single:This is a single line element with <span:more> <span:than> <span:one> element
  <multi:This is a single line element that
    actually spans more than one line so it should be rendered as multi-line

  <single:
    This single line element has en empty first line, so it will be single-line anyway

  <multi
    this is a multi-line element, only if it has a single line
# EOF
